<div class="uk-grid">
	<div class="uk-width-large-1-3">
		<div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box">
			<h3 class="uk-panel-title">Step 1</h3>
			<p>Create your account.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="uk-width-large-1-3">
		<div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box uk-panel-box-primary">
			<h3 class="uk-panel-title">Step 2</h3>
			<p>Configure your main password.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="uk-width-large-1-3">
		<div class="uk-panel uk-panel-box">
			<h3 class="uk-panel-title">Step 3</h3>
			<p>Welcome!</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<p>In this second step, you must choose your main password.</p>

<form action="/user/sign-up-step-2" class="uk-form uk-form-horizontal" method="POST">
	<%- myForm.toHTML(uikitFieldHorizontal) %>
	<div class="uk-alert uk-alert-danger uk-alert-large">
		<h2>Important</h2>
		<p>This password is the most important, it is used to crypt/decrypt your passwords.<br/>If you lose it, all data are lost, there is no way to find it, only you know it!</p>
		<p>Please be carefull by choosing it, and do not share it with anyone!</p>
	</div>
	<div class="uk-form-row">
		<div class="uk-form-controls">
			<button class="uk-button uk-button-primary" type="submit">Set the main password</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</form>